label: Category: Gypsum Boards

products.description_short: Knauf Regular Gypsum Boards are gypsum based wallboards whose front and back surfaces, and long edges, are sandwiched in a board liner. Knauf RG boards are used for cladding walls and ceilings constructed on metal grids and wooden frames: for furring, partitions and ceilings, prefab building units and for dry lining using dot and dab of a gypsum based bonder. Knauf Regular Gypsum Boards comply fully with the requirements of DIN 18180-GKB, EN520-Type A Gypsum Wallboard.
products.name: Knauf RG Gypsum Board 1200x2400x15mm
